<h2>Recherches récentes en FLE  (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1278'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
<h4>Herausgeber</h4>
<span class='tag multiline'>Alain Kamber</span>
<span class='tag multiline'>Carine Skupien Dekens</span>
<p class='space-l'></p>
